# Changelog

To install the unreleased climux version, see [developmental releases](https://climux.git-pull.com/quickstart.html#developmental-releases).

[pip](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/):

```console
$ pip install --user --upgrade --pre climux
```

[uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/):

```console
$ uv add climux --prerelease allow
```

